itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway welcome back special guest Dr. Frank to discuss the importance of testosterone replacement therapy (TRT), why so many men come back from fighting overseas have low testosterone levels, how you can combat it, and why your local family physicians might not be giving you the correct information that you need.  You can call the Frank Institute at 910-679-8534.
